product_name: Keen Brooklyn II Travel Bag - Women's
long_description: Carry all you need for the day in the women's popular Keen Brooklyn II Canvas Travel Bag, whether you're commuting downtown or leaving town altogether for the weekend. Made of durable nylon with a highly water-resistant, environmentally friendly coating. Roomy interior holds a lot of gear, such as a water bottle, umbrella and lunch. Rear exterior pocket is great for magazines, boarding passes or a paperback. Adjustable shoulder strap has recycled-aluminum components. Keen Brooklyn II Travel Bag has a front organizer and drop-in pockets.
